  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether acupuncture is helpful for patients with
      joint pain associated with psoriasis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this study, patients with psoriasis and joint pain will receive either real acupuncture or
      sham acupuncture to see if acupuncture can be an effective treatment of joint pain in
      patients with psoriasis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
